Mayor's Office > Speeches


Speeches

        Speeches

           Houston is a great city, run by dedicated employees and supported by
           its citizens, and Mayor Lee P. Brown holds the distinction of being the
           representative for all of them. If you follow the link on the left you
           will find Mayor Brown's speeches, delivered over the course of each day
           as he strives to meet the needs of the City, covering the issues and
           topics that concern Houstonians.


